                     <msItem xml:id="MS_Bodl_285-item-3">
                        <locus from="166">(fol. 166)</locus>
                        <rubric>Vita sancti Petri Tharentasiensis
                           archiepiscopi &amp; Confessoris</rubric>
                        <note>In a different hand. By 'Gaufridus abbas': preceded by three
                           documents about the Life as printed in the Bollandist Acta Sanctorum for
                           May 8 ( = May ii. 322-3), and a list of chapters: at end 'Finit ubi non
                           est finis'. Then follow (fol. 180) five letters about the canonization of
                           the archbishop (as above, May ii. 345-7), and the Bulla canonizationis
                           (ibid. 347): at fol. 183v is added in a 14th cent. hand another
                           'miraculum de usurario' done by the archbishop, partly injured.</note>
                     </msItem>
